Create MilestonesList component:
- Displays milestones with deliverable submission and approval workflow
- Per-milestone deliverable management with status tracking (pending_review, approved, revision_requested)
- Brand can approve or request revisions on milestone deliverables
- Creator can submit deliverables to specific milestones
- Shows milestone completion status and escrow release information
- Inline deliverable submission form for creators

Update CollaborationDetails to support both workflows:
- Detect milestone-based collaborations via has_milestones flag
- Conditionally render MilestonesList for brief/campaign collaborations
- Keep existing package-based deliverable UI for package collaborations
- Hide revision policy and revision history for milestone-based collaborations

This enables proper deliverable workflow for brief and campaign collaborations
with milestone-based escrow releases (30-day clearance per milestone).

